WEBVTT

00:00:01.072 --> 00:00:03.880
Nataka niwaambie kisa 
kuhusu msichana mmoja.

00:00:04.515 --> 00:00:06.627
Lakini siwezi kuwaambia jina lake halisi.

00:00:07.015 --> 00:00:08.928
Hivyo tufanye kumuita Hadiza.

00:00:09.561 --> 00:00:11.050
Hadiza ana miaka 20.

00:00:11.639 --> 00:00:12.790
Ana aibu,

00:00:12.814 --> 00:00:16.048
lakini ana tabasamu zuri 
ambalo hufanya uso wake kung'aa

00:00:16.959 --> 00:00:18.889
Lakini yuko katika maumivu wakati wote.

00:00:20.643 --> 00:00:24.117
Na anaweza kuwa 
mtu wa matibabu maisha yake yote.

00:00:25.046 --> 00:00:26.551
Je wataka kujua kwa nini?

00:00:27.964 --> 00:00:30.821
Hadiza ni msichana wa Chibok,